sentences: Jamie Arentzen (born November 22, 1970) is a member of the alternative rock band American Hi-Fi and lead guitarist for Miley Cyrus.
In the spring of 2009, he also played with Butch Walker's band, Butch Walker and the Let's Go Out Tonites.
Guitars: 1970 Les Paul Deluxe Goldtop, Fender Jazzmaster, Gibson Flying V, 1963 Gibson SG Junior
